languages.text: "Члены экипажа сторонятся меня, и это ожидаемо. Облик членов Навис Нобилите вселяет ужас в сердца простых обывателей".
"The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

languages.text: “所有船员都躲着我，我并不意外。但凡导航宗族成员露面，普通人总是会恐惧不已。”
languages.original_text: "The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

languages.text: « Les membres de l'équipage m'évitent autant que faire se peut, mais je m'y attendais. L'apparence des membres de la Navis Nobilite instille généralement la terreur dans le cœur des gens du commun. »
languages.original_text: "The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

traits.locale_text: « Les membres de l'équipage m'évitent autant que faire se peut, mais je m'y attendais. L'apparence des membres de la Navis Nobilite instille généralement la terreur dans le cœur des gens du commun. »

languages.text: «La tripulación me evita, como cabría esperar. El aspecto de los miembros de la Navis Nobilite siembra el terror en la gente corriente».
languages.original_text: "The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

traits.locale_text: «La tripulación me evita, como cabría esperar. El aspecto de los miembros de la Navis Nobilite siembra el terror en la gente corriente».

languages.text: 「乗組員たちから避けられるのは、予想できていたことです。航宙貴族の姿は、一般市民の心に恐怖を植え付けるものですから」
languages.original_text: "The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

traits.locale_text: 「乗組員たちから避けられるのは、予想できていたことです。航宙貴族の姿は、一般市民の心に恐怖を植え付けるものですから」

languages.text: "Die Crewmitglieder meiden mich, was auch zu erwarten ist. Das Erscheinen eines Mitglieds der Navis Nobilite erfüllt die Herzen des Pöbels mit Angst."
languages.original_text: "The crew members shun me, and that is to be expected. The appearance of members of the Navis Nobilite instils terror in the hearts of common people."

languages.text: "Tayfalar beni azarladı. Bu duruma şaşırmadım. Navis Nobilite mensuplarının varlığı, avamın yüreğine korku saçıyor."
